Name: ORBIT
checklistText:
1. Emer Retro Seq Fuse - OFF
2. Emer Drogue Deploy Fuse - OFF
3. Landing Bag switch - AUTO OFF
4. Retro Delay switch - NORM
5. Retro Manual fuse - OFF
6. Retro Tower/Sep Cap telelights - OUT
(5 min after Sep Cap)
7. DC Volts knob - MAIN
8. All instruments - CHECK

9. If out-of-range from radio station, set UHF PWR - HI for longer reach
